_sText:
I thought i was done mapping.
I was wrong.
compile time 2 minutes 10 seconds.
mapping time 4 hours or so.
this map is smaller, fast game play with tactics involved. 
I have added my exploding car to bring some excitement to the map.
most objects are func_detail to help the frates.
this is in dev_textures, and yes i plan on coloring it.
There is fog, environment lighting, models, and light effects.
No there is no 3d skybox, or hdr.
Yes they would fit very nicely here.

Please give this map an assessment for design and fun. or anythign else it makes you think of.

Install to your cstrike/maps folder
